        "subject": "LU-19860 mdc: fix missing mutex_unlock in chlg_obd_get()",
        "message": "LU-19860 mdc: fix missing mutex_unlock in chlg_obd_get()\n\nchlg_obd_get() acquires chlg_registered_dev_lock but fails\nto release it when ced_obds list is empty, returning NULL\nwith the mutex still held. This causes a deadlock for any\nsubsequent caller attempting to acquire the same mutex.\n\nAdd the missing mutex_unlock() call before returning NULL.\n\nTest-Parameters: trivial\nSigned-off-by: Sohei Koyama <skoyama@ddn.com>\nChange-Id: I8871254b077923178be5cce0d3b1b0386f3242da\nReviewed-on: https://review.whamcloud.com/c/fs/lustre-release/+/63849\nTested-by: Maloo <maloo@whamcloud.com>\nReviewed-by: Andreas Dilger <adilger@thelustrecollective.com>\nReviewed-by: Oleg Drokin <green@whamcloud.com>\nReviewed-by: James Simmons <jsimmons@infradead.org>\nTested-by: jenkins <devops@whamcloud.com>\nReviewed-by: Hongchao Zhang <hongchao@whamcloud.com>\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
